Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take back Sanji who was being pressed into a marriage\Nand left his friends behind,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others infiltrated the Whole Cake Island\Nwhere Emperor Big Mom is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy has separated from Nami, Chopper and Carrot\Nin the Seducing Woods.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Sanji got into a \Nfight with Vinsmoke Judge,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his father and Germa 66's generalissimo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a sacrifice, Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think of you as my son even one bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you try to get off of this island,\Nyour hands will be blown off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At the same time,\NBrook and Pedro were secretly on the move...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...to get Big Mom's Road Ponegliff\Nwhich is one of the keys to the One Piece.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"A Giant Ambition!\NBig Mom and Caesar!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:56.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,SOMEWHERE AROUND THE CAPITAL - SWEET CITY
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Extra! Extra!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss Jimbei betrayed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This happened between him and Mama yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss Jimbei was sure cool\Nwhen he stopped Mama's tantrum.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He blustered that he \Nwanted to leave her crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.52,0:05:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he got scared of paying \Nthe price and backed down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? That's pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.94,0:05:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't he know how much he benefitted\Nfrom being one of Emperor Big Mom's subordinates?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's known as the "First Son of the Sea" for nothing.\NI lost respect for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he was a coward as well as a traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.83,0:05:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jimbei-san,\NI didn't know you were working under Big Mom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why the Fish-Man Island\Nwas protected by Big Mom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei is a former Warlord, isn't he?\NI can't believe someone of his stature is her subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook, do you know this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he's a very important person to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.69,0:06:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Jimbei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Join...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.49,0:06:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I fulfill my duties\Nand am free from them,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise I will come to see you all again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.42,0:06:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you haven't changed your mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can I take you up on your offer then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess he turned down the offer to join our crew\Nthat day{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}because he wanted to fulfill \Nhis duty to Big Mom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, this article...\NIt doesn't sound like something he'd do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Won't he come see us again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.45,0:06:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.95,0:06:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! I have to go somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing is more important to you now\Nthan choosing a dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being such a baby-{\i1}s'il vous pla√Æt{\i0},\NPudding-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pudding-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it looks good on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this one? I knew it, Pudding-{\i1}sama{\i0}!\NIt looks wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything looks good on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one do you like, Pudding-{\i1}sama{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pudding-{\i1}sama{\i0},\Ndo you know what the groom likes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!\NNo! I've only met him once so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.75,0:07:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, Pudding-{\i1}san{\i0},\Nwhat is she doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she got caught by her attendants.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assumed she'd already led Sanji-{\i1}san{\i0} out\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to meet with Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0} and the others by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at this, I bet\NSanji doesn't even know that we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:08:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, who did Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0} see at the shore?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.\NMaybe he just saw someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... If I'm not mistaken,\Nhe was on Big Mom's ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know him very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.07,0:08:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baron Tamago!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baron Tamago, may I speak to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it-{\i1}soir{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hat's ship that stopped by\Nat Chocolat Town yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They already know!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When they left, Mr. Pekoms who was guiding them\Nwas already gone, they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.81,0:08:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They know everything!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the four Straw Hats\Nwho wandered into the Seducing Woods today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're already cornered!\NThey're as good as captured!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:09:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy-san and the others got caught?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.91,0:09:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still can't find the remaining two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's leaked out completely!\NThey knew everything from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were they watching us from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:21.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A PANTHER MINK
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That mink is not a panther-{\i1}soir{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a jaguar Mink. His name is Pedro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little bit from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.28,0:09:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what he would do-{\i1}feuille{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Anyway, I want you guys to look for Pekoms.\N--Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.46,0:09:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pekoms. Since he was alive-{\i1}bon{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the sake of our \Nlong-standing partnership,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:09:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to ask for \NMama's pardon with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He gives me a lot of trouble-{\i1}marron{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are in big trouble!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:13.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE NORTHEAST COAST OF THE WHOLE CAKE ISLAND
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, cut it out, junior!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!\NHow many times do I have to tell you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's laughing! That's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:32.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,CHARLOTTE CHIFFON - BEGE'S WIFE\NTHE 22ND DAUGHTER OF THE CHARLOTTE FAMILY
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CAPONE "GANG" PEZ - BEGE'S SON
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good, good, good! You're a good boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:41.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,CAPONE "GANG" BEGE\NTHE CAPTAIN OF THE FIRETANK PIRATES
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, junior.\NI hope you'll become a great boss like me one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand watching that! Grr!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.94,0:10:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dazzling, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was just born.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's an exquisite contrast?\NIt's like a painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what you chose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pekoms. I gave you a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.67,0:11:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't look like a chance to me. Grr!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what happened to you in Zou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They saved my family members and friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Human empathy is useless shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not cut out for this business.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.66,0:11:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the perfect place \Nfor getting rid of someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any last words?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You underestimate Mama too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:04.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE SOUTHWEST COAST - THE SEDUCING WOODS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.16,0:13:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Sanji! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's wrong with you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop running!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.91,0:13:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Finger Net!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:14:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't run anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's waiting for you.\NLet's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two Sanjis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,THE WHOLE CAKE CHATEAU
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.27,0:14:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,THE QUEEN'S CHAMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I invested enough money,\NCaesar Clown.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-Y-Y-Yes!\NAnd of course, I didn't stop researching!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dream! My dream is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for all races in the \Nworld to become family
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and sit around a dining table\Nat the same eye level.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll drink what I drink,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and eat what I eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.92,0:16:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a wonderful dream?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're gonna make it come true for me,\NCaesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to make my family members gigantic\Nwith the power of science.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You kept telling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that you were almost done\Nbut you needed a little more research money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was excited and\Nspent quite a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how're the results?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.42,0:16:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thanks to you, they're quite good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The gigantification of the human body.\NYes, I was doing experiments.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The whole world is\Nlooking for a technology like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:17:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I was performing experiments\Nto turn kids into giants. It was deadly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm a genius scientist.\NI knew the results from the beginning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's impossible to make a drug \Nthat'll magically make people
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,gigantic like this old bag wants.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why I just screwed her out of her money\Nand...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...called girls' ships over to the island\Nevery night,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and spent all the money on alcohol and women!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those were the good old days!\NI was going nuts behind Joker's back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DOFLAMINGO FALLS!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't expect Joker to be defeated...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:18:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and my life to become this miserable!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit! All was smooth sailing before!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is all because of that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you giving a facial performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This! And that! And everything!\NThey're all Straw Hat Luffy's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Mom! I was doing the research\Nwithout taking time for sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.14,0:18:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was almost completed when...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Straw Hat and Trafalgar Law appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't for them,\Nthe Gigantism Drug would've been completed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.16,0:18:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame that the lab \Nbuilt by the World Government
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with such a high level of \Ntechnology was destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could only achieve the results\Nin that perfectly controlled environment!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The vast amount of money you invested\Nand that lab!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.89,0:19:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost them so I can't create\Nthe Gigantism Drug now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.16,0:19:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I built the exact same lab\Nas the one on Punk Hazard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.04,0:19:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had the blueprint long before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.21,0:19:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Minister of Candy\Ncan make anything out of candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can spend as much money as you want\Nfor the research.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.89,0:19:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A-A-A... A-Are you sure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I appreciate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:19:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"So?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.99,0:20:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When will it be ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.87,0:20:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In a week? Or two weeks?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.63,0:20:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't be ridiculous!\NMankind has been doing the research for centuries,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but no one's ever succeeded!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lick! Lick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.61,0:20:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like that, Caesar-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.61,0:20:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to be quite authentic, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.87,0:20:50.20,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,CHARLOTTE PEROSPERO - THE MINISTER OF CANDY\NTHE ELDEST SON OF THE CHARLOTTE FAMILY\NA CANDY HUMAN WHO ATE THE LICK-LICK FRUIT
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The inside is exactly like \Nthe way it was too. Lick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.83,0:20:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No! Don't do that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.38,0:21:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've arrived at the Whole Cake Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go-{\i1}rero{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.24,0:21:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Hey, Black-Foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.53,0:21:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me back my heart before you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.53,0:21:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.93,0:21:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only have two weeks to\Nproduce the Gigantism Drug!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:21:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it takes longer than that,\NI'll turn you into a "candy man" and lick you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.57,0:22:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A candy man?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.28,0:22:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll be killed! I'll be killed in two weeks!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.04,0:22:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I gotta do something!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.38,0:22:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have seen you like dozens of times now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.01,0:22:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's you again.\N--I found another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.35,0:22:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.78,0:22:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.22,0:23:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you guys multiply?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.69,0:23:26.92,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Mom's extraordinary ability allows her
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.92,0:23:29.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,to create a world of dreams and madness!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.40,0:23:32.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The singing flowers, the romping snacks,\Nand the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.05,0:23:34.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,trees that attack Luffy and \Nthe others in the woods...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.20,0:23:37.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those mysterious creatures of Totto Land have
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.04,0:23:39.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,a stunning secret in their lives \Nand now it comes to light!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.33,0:23:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"The Land of Souls! Mom's Fatal Ability!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.96,0:23:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.80,0:23:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.80,0:23:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
